sources.title: Freedom Strike | FULL MOVIE | Action, Thriller | Michael Dudikoff
sources.description:
When a peace treaty between America and Syria is thwarted, the renegade head of the Syrian army retaliates. He steals a nuclear weapon that only the Freedom Strike team can stop! Cue an action-packed race against time to save the world.

Michael Dudikoff; Tom Dickson, 
Tone Loc; Tyler Haynes, 
Felicity Waterman; Maddie Reese, 
Jay Anthony; Col. Rama, 
Nicolas Coster; Adam Torrance, 
James Karen; President Mitchell, 
Michael Fairman; Gen Porter, 
Frank Roman; Casey Billups, 
Penny Peyser; Linda, 
Ron Harper; Norman, 
Sean Holland; Gary, 
James Van Patten; Tactical Action Officer, 
William Langlois; Captain Mehl, 
John Putch; Stanley Shaw

1998
Directed by Jerry P. Jacobs
